description: A local to Orange County, Mustache Mike’s Italian Ice offers 120 flavors of silky, smooth and creamy delicious frozen fruit treats for your special events. We take pride in our 100 year old secret recipe that adds the “wow” factor to our Italian ice. Equipped with our clean mobile trucks, we give you only the highest quality product with a personalized family style service that you will enjoy. Our ice cart is available to cater private events as well!Some of our flavors: •"Da bomb" (Cherry, lemon, and blue raspberry)•"Big daddy" (Orange, pineapple, and cherry)•Juicy Rancher (Sour apple, watermelon, and lemon)•Strawberry-banana•Watermelon•Mango•Root Beer Float•Chocolate•Sour Apple•Cherry•Lemon•Blue Raspberry •And many, many more!
name: Mustache Mike's
